coming back? ♪

42:05.392 --> 42:09.744
♪ I'm waiting

42:11.877 --> 42:15.924
♪ Haven't had a dream
in a long time ♪

42:17.317 --> 42:20.059
♪ Haven't been able to sleep

42:20.102 --> 42:22.017
Sergeant Winters,
glad you could join us.

42:22.061 --> 42:25.020
BOMAN:
♪ Are you coming back?

42:25.064 --> 42:27.762
♪ Are you coming back?

42:27.806 --> 42:31.200
♪ I'm waiting

42:38.164 --> 42:41.863
Have you thought more
about what we talked about?

42:41.907 --> 42:44.039
I have.

42:44.083 --> 42:45.606
And?

42:47.826 --> 42:50.045
I want what you want.

42:57.009 --> 43:01.013
BOMAN: ♪ I want you more
